      heading: 'Example Etsy Puzzle Shop Catalog Layout',
      content: 'Here is a concrete example of how to structure an Etsy puzzle shop with 30 initial listings organized across 6 shop sections, using outputs from all 4 puzzle generators.\n\nShop section one \u2014 Word Search Puzzles (10 listings): Animal Word Search Pack (5 puzzles, $2.99), Food and Cooking Word Search (5 puzzles, $2.99), Ocean and Sea Life Word Search (5 puzzles, $2.99), Animal Word Search Collection (12 puzzles at 3 difficulty levels, $5.99), Holiday Word Search Bundle (15 puzzles across 4 holidays, $6.99), Back-to-School Vocabulary Word Search (10 puzzles, $4.99), Large Print Word Search for Seniors (8 puzzles, $4.99), Science Vocabulary Word Search (8 puzzles, $3.99), Sports Word Search Pack (5 puzzles, $2.99), and Word Search Mega Pack (50 puzzles across all themes, $12.99). Word search as your primary section should have the most listings.\n\nShop section two \u2014 Crossword Puzzles (5 listings): follows the same top-performing themes as word search. Animal Crossword Pack (5 puzzles, $2.99), Holiday Crossword Bundle (10 puzzles, $4.99), Science Vocabulary Crossword (5 puzzles, $2.99), Crossword Collection (20 puzzles, $6.99), and Crossword Mega Pack (40 puzzles, $9.99).\n\nShop section three \u2014 Word Scrambles (4 listings): Animal Word Scramble (8 puzzles, $2.99), Holiday Word Scramble Bundle (12 puzzles, $4.99), Vocabulary Scramble Collection (20 puzzles, $5.99), and Word Scramble Mega Pack (35 puzzles, $7.99). Word scrambles serve as quick companion activities.\n\nShop section four \u2014 Cryptograms (3 listings): Animal Cryptogram Puzzles (5 puzzles, $2.99), Mystery Code Puzzle Collection (15 puzzles, $5.99), and Cryptogram Mega Pack (30 puzzles, $8.99). Cryptograms appeal to older students and adult puzzle fans.\n\nShop section five \u2014 Multi-Format Bundles (5 listings): Animal Puzzle Party (word search + crossword + scramble + cryptogram, 20 puzzles, $9.99), Holiday Puzzle Collection (all 4 formats across 4 holidays, 30 puzzles, $12.99), Science Puzzle Pack (all 4 formats, 20 puzzles, $9.99), Classroom Puzzle Kit (word search + crossword + scramble, 25 puzzles, $8.99), and Ultimate Puzzle Library (100+ puzzles across all formats and themes, $19.99).\n\nShop section six \u2014 Seasonal Puzzles (3 listings): Halloween Puzzle Pack (all 4 formats, $6.99), Christmas Puzzle Collection (all 4 formats, $7.99), and Summer Activity Puzzle Bundle (all 4 formats, $7.99). These rotate based on seasonal timing.\n\nThis 30-listing catalog covers multiple search terms, price points, formats, and buyer segments while creating clear upgrade paths from individual packs to multi-format bundles and mega collections.',
